section.para:
            The qualifier @JmsDestination is available to decorate JNDI oriented objects.  This includes instances of javax.jms.Destination
            as well as MessageConsumers and MessageProducers.
         
            
@Inject @JmsDestination(jndiName="jms/MyTopic") Topic t;
@Inject @JmsDestination(jndiName="jms/MyQueue") Queue q;
